<!ELEMENT MovieCollection (artists, genres, movies)>
<!ELEMENT artists (artist+)>
<!ELEMENT artist (name)>
<!ATTLIST artist id ID #REQUIRED directed IDREFS #IMPLIED acted_in IDREFS #IMPLIED>
<!ELEMENT name (#PCDATA)>

<!ELEMENT genres (genre+)>
<!ELEMENT genre (#PCDATA)>
<!ATTLIST genre id ID #REQUIRED>

<!ELEMENT movies (movie+)>
<!ELEMENT movie (
    title, poster, year, age_restriction,
    length, rating, description, 
    budget, gross_worldwide
    )>
<!ATTLIST movie 
    id ID #REQUIRED
    director IDREF #REQUIRED
    stars IDREFS #REQUIRED
    genres IDREFS #IMPLIED>
<!ELEMENT title (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT poster EMPTY>
<!ATTLIST poster image ENTITY #REQUIRED>
<!ELEMENT year (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT age_restriction (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT length (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT rating (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT description (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT budget (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT gross_worldwide (#PCDATA)>

